## Community & Membership

The community of E.I. Werner lives inside The Outside Inn. That's the architecture: E.I. Werner is the public-facing work; The Outside Inn is the community layer — the Discord, the membership tiers, the patron roll that runs on every stream. The inn is the place. The Innsiders and Innkeeps are the people in it.

Everything runs through Fourthwall. One platform, one brand experience, one URL. Discord handles community. Signal handles the inner circle.

