### Credit Roll Logic

All members — Innsiders and Innkeeps — appear in video and stream credits in order of joining. Number 1 joined before number 2. Lower numbers are earlier. Innkeeps are visually distinct from Innsiders in the roll — the distinction is design-level, not loud. Visual language to be finalized with Luiz or Marwan before the patron roll goes live with real members.

### Writing Review — How It Works

After 7 consecutive months as an Innkeep, the perk unlocks. The member submits via a Google Form: name, badge number, 777 words max, and agreement to stream review. Evan reviews it live on stream — out loud, in real time, honest. The stream requirement is not a condition to minimize the perk. It is the perk. The member gets a public, documented moment where their work was taken seriously. The audience gets genuine craft content. The form link goes out via Signal when the 7-month mark hits. No queue, no async back-and-forth, no DMs.

### Store Upsell

Any order over $30 triggers an offer of a free first month of Innsider membership at checkout. The 14% Innsider discount applies immediately to that same order. Set-and-forget in Fourthwall — do not edit once live without contacting Fourthwall support.

