### The Pricing Logic

$7.77 and $21.21. Base-7 runs through the entire fantasy world. The prices carry that DNA. $7.77 is elevated enough to not feel like a tip jar. $21.21 is a real commitment that justifies real access. The discounts follow the same logic: 14% and 21%. Everything is divisible by seven. The sevens are not decoration — they are the cosmology made visible in the commerce.

