## Leadership Philosophy

Evan wants to be the kind of project leader people want to work for — not just someone who pays on time, but someone whose projects people are proud to be part of.

**The upside principle:** People who deliver great work should have upside if that work resonates. The royalty structures are the first expression of this.

**The commitment:** Find ways to share upside that are financially responsible at this stage. Always look for the version of the deal where great work gets rewarded beyond the flat fee.

**The debrief habit:** Evan keeps all collaborators in the loop after milestones. The people who built the assets that made something possible should know it worked.

