## Open Questions & Gaps

### Writing Stream Structure

Still the core creative challenge. The 7:07 AM March 4 stream was the first live test. Still needs: clear opening, visible session goal, audience engagement built in without turning it into a tutorial. The answer comes from reps. Track what works in Athens.

### Gaming Integration Energy

Does gaming WITH community after writing energize or drain? The first few weeks in Athens will answer this. If it drains, the gaming portion can shrink or become optional.

### The Human Layer

The workshop framework requires at least five non-business, non-manufactured elements. Still not inventoried. Scheduled for next version.

### Painful Problem Validation

16 problems listed, still unvalidated. Wednesday is the first real test with a meaningful audience. Update with actual language people use once signal exists.

### The Unsolved Thing

Evan was asked what he's most uncertain about. He didn't answer. This placeholder stays until he does.

### ONCE Release Format

Writing purity first. Packaging decisions later.

### Merch Resolution Standards

Need to formalize minimum DPI, pixel dimensions per product size, color profile requirements for all future commissions. Build this into the Luiz product catalog brief.

### Stream Topics Prep

Need to brainstorm with Claude: how to talk about tech career and time at SKIMS consistently. What's the right framing? What's the version of that story that serves the brand and the audience, not just the resume?

### Outside Inn Second Channel — Active Evaluation

The architecture is settled: the Outside Inn is the community layer, and the second channel is part of that layer. Not formally launching yet. In Athens: if an unscheduled stream happens, the Outside Inn channel is the right home. The ambient broadcast lives there when it's ready. Evaluate whether to formally activate after the first few Athens weeks.

### Blast List Categories

For Wednesday personal texts: extended gaming friends, IRL college friends, SKIMS people, family, others? List needs to be finalized before Monday.

### Athens Writing + Stream Structure

Full structured writing goals and stream goals for the entire Athens deployment need to be mapped before Wednesday. Think of every session as both a live stream and a future VOD. Prepare accordingly.

